    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>GameBreak</strong> is a lively indie local-multiplayer mini-game collection packed with <strong>five</strong> wild and wonderfully different games—each designed for exactly <strong>two players</strong>.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121960/extras/ce0a7a50920a993e4b2548bb1497186b.avif?t=1771608493\" width=668 height=244 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> Each game has it's own mechanics and gameplay. You can challenge each other by surviving, racing, shooting or finishing a puzzle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121960/extras/684014c96bcf542096968251721cfb53.poster.avif?t=1771608493\" width=626 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121960/extras/684014c96bcf542096968251721cfb53.webm?t=1771608493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121960/extras/684014c96bcf542096968251721cfb53.mp4?t=1771608493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Each game is crafted to challenge your speed, spark your creativity, and put your patience to the test.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121960/extras/ba06a8fc76951f55de5dc53c6d89fa26.poster.avif?t=1771608493\" width=626 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121960/extras/ba06a8fc76951f55de5dc53c6d89fa26.webm?t=1771608493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2121960/extras/ba06a8fc76951f55de5dc53c6d89fa26.mp4?t=1771608493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The whole experience is all about light-hearted fun and friendly, local play—perfect for partners, family members, or friends who just want to laugh, compete, and enjoy the moment together. <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take a Break and Play.</p>",
